'''Hotard''' is an [[i see what you did there|oh so clever]] combination of "[[whore|ho]]" and "[[retard|tard]]" and a way to shave a whole syllable off of "stupid slut".  Definitely ''not'' the rather humorous name of a charter coach service in [[New Orleans]].

